# pooled connection string from the Neon `seed-sandbox` branch.
#
# Format (Neon gives you this in the dashboard under "Connection details"):
#   postgresql://<user>:<password>@<host>-pooler.<region>.aws.neon.tech/neondb?sslmode=require

